{"tid":1883823,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本厚生勞動省職員確診   曾在「鑽石公主號」工作","createTime":"2020-02-17T08:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T08:17:15.000Z","uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"84a6bd692c6ba11b1eb9b91a32f41fb0269453d9","tid":1883823,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T08:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509035-20200217.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509035-20200217.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ4lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=f566f2ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509035-20200217.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9546a00f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509035-20200217.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n日本新增兩宗新型肺炎病例，其中一人是曾經在「鑽石公主號」郵輪上工作的厚生勞動省職員。<br />\n<br />\n當局說，染病的50多歲男職員，上星期二開始在船上收集資料，再向當局匯報，但無接觸過乘客或船員，該名職員星期二當日，亦曾經安排確診患者落船，與患者距離最少兩米。除了這名職員，一名曾經在郵輪上工作的檢疫官，早前亦確診。<br />\n<br />\n另一名新增患者是神奈川縣一間醫院的女護士，她曾經在醫院照顧一名80多歲女病人，這名病人死後確診感染。"}]}